{
  "stem": "13690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will try to-- to hire a horse and a buggy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe the man-- the other man has a horse and a buggy, and I will pick-- pick you up and put you in a wagon.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You'll be able to walk.'",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A good idea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We looked at the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, 'Eli, it's 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When will you-- how long will it take you?'",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, 'Look, it will take me maybe an hour to go one way, an hour the other way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Figure an hour to convince the guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By 12 o'clock, definitely, I will be back.' 12 o'clock passed by.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me just go back one second-- while we were there, we didn't have anything what to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so we had a bottle with honey, but the bottle was dry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The honey dries.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to take a stick from a pine tree and dipped it in, and Mother gave each child just to suck a little bit of that honey.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not that we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just-- it's a mother's instinct to give the children something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She didn't have anything else to give, so she gave just to suck this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When Eli went back to the village, and you left-- you were left with your mother and your sister, were you hiding in the woods?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you on the riverbank?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Describe, where were you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were already away from the river, deep inside the inland already, inside to the east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hiding in a ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he covered us with branches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said that he knows exactly where he's dropping us off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when it was 12 o'clock, 1 o'clock, 2 o'clock, 4 o'clock, 5 o'clock in the evening, we do not see Eli.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
